### Animation Priority

1. Native Tailwind: `animate-pulse`, `animate-spin`, `animate-bounce`
2. Transitions: `transition-colors duration-200`
3. Existing: `fade-in`, `services-reveal` (in `global.css`)
4. New keyframes: Only if explicitly requested (include `prefers-reduced-motion`)

